  "id": "BIT-openbao-2026-40264",
  "summary": "OpenBao's Token Store Allows Cross-Namespace Renewal, Revocation",
  "details": "OpenBao is an open source identity-based secrets management system. OpenBao's namespaces provide multi-tenant separation. Prior to version 2.5.3, a tenant who leaks token accessors can have their token revoked or renewed by a privileged administrator in another tenant. This is addressed in v2.5.3.",
